  POST /runs                   -> Run (creates and optionally awaits)
  GET  /runs/{run_id}          -> Run
  DELETE /runs/{run_id}        -> 204 (cancel)
  GET  /runs/{run_id}/await    -> SSE stream of RunOutputEvent

